
'''''Drexciya'''''   ni filimi yo muri [[Gana]] yasohotse 2010 akaba documentary film ntoya  yayoboye na Akosua Adoma Owusu afatanije na California Institute wa Arts (CalArts). Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu ikinamico mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi Rotterdam 2011 kandi yitabira ''Video ya Changing Same'' mu nzu ndangamurage ya Studio i Harlem, muri New York .

== Inyandiko ==
''Drexciya''   yerekana ikigo cyo koga rusange cyatawe giherereye i Accra, muri [[Gana]] cyashyizwe kuri Riviera. Riviera icyarimwe yari iterambere ridasanzwe, rigizwe nizamuka ryiza cyane hamwe na hoteri yinyenyeri eshanu. Kuva mu myaka ya za 70, Riviera yaguye mubihe bidasanzwe. Iyi documentaire ngufi yahumetswe n imigani ya afro-futurist yakwirakwijwe nitsinda rya Drexciya ryitwa Detroit. Bavuga ko Drexciya ari umugani w’amazi utuwe n’abana bataravuka b’abagore b’abanyafrika bajugunywe mu nyanja mu gihe cy’ubucuruzi bw’abacakara ba Trans-Atlantike. Aba bana bamenyereye kandi bahinduka kugirango bahumeke mumazi.

